{"tid":492241,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[叫春]我好撚辛苦","createTime":"2017-12-07T10:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T11:40:30.000Z","uid":32324,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2e32b64022619d4e73c0bf9e50da5f9d5fa9a795","tid":492241,"uid":32324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:45:57.000Z","msg":"對左成九年 一晚一通電話就一拍兩散<br />\n仲要blame我話我殘忍話我仆街話我自私<br />\n有無諗過一路以黎我對你幾大容忍<br />\n係你一路苛索一路要求我 我做唔到想放棄想分開<br />\n點解可以推翻個責任比我？<br />\n我理性上叫自己收手 <br />\n但成屋都係你啲衫褲 你送比我既生日禮物 你寄比我既信同卡 你畫比我既畫 你錄比我既歌<br />\n尋日行過outback我仲記得你話下次一齊同我食<br />\n今日諗住買機票一月去旅行睇雪 又諗起當初話過要一齊去<br />\n太多太多 我根本每行一步每睇一眼既野全部都有你既存在<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">算啦我都係除帽吧啦 叫春完畢</span></span>"},{"pid":"91268bc1dd54caab7200b79bab12419def5d58df","tid":492241,"uid":142707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:47:53.000Z","msg":"Ching講多d點帽法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571e8562f9eb8051e704da71ece54572806ab88f","tid":492241,"uid":32324,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:50:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ching講多d點帽法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你同揭我瘡疤有咩分別"},{"pid":"e3f5b40f1c33e49cb42b93ae258f82d8f5c0a4bd","tid":492241,"uid":72739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:52:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Ching講多d點帽法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你同揭我瘡疤有咩分別</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講啦"},{"pid":"8fba8406b8ad115f632af02abbafc20c55449347","tid":492241,"uid":136502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:58:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Ching講多d點帽法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你同揭我瘡疤有咩分別</blockquote><br />\n你唔講 發洩唔到㗎"},{"pid":"d6a62039630b2139a293cbfa930cf7276c90d17e","t